column2: SELECT p.psfMag_u, p.psfMag_g, p.psfMag_r, p.psfMag_i, p.psfMag_z, d.w1mpro, d.w2mpro, d.w3mpro, d.w4mpro FROM PhotoObjAll AS p JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (#, #, #) AS GN ON p.objID = GN.objID LEFT JOIN WISE_xmatch as c on p.ObjID = c.sdss_objid LEFT JOIN WISE_allsky as d on c.wise_cntr = d.cntr
